      <description>&lt;p&gt;Flickr&#39;s edit in place behaviors make it easy to change data on records without requiring the round trip to a full page editor form. They provided one of the earliest examples of this behavior, using AJAX to quickly update fields in place, and has remained the model to emulate for some time.&lt;/p&gt;
